This was by far the worst sub I've ever ordered period that was definitely not worth the price. I read a bad review on it previously and decided to give it a fair chance, this was a big mistake. Their cuts of frozen beef patties are riddled with gummy-like glycerin filler that has a horrible taste, grey color and texture with little to no genuine beef. You're better off making a dog food sub. None the less, the cheesesteak I previously had was good for the price and a far cry from this tragedy. Take my advice and never order the cheeseburger sub, your wallet and digestive system will regret it severely.
